snippet.title: Dumb Ways to Die 4: Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Your favourite Beans are back in Dumb Ways to Die 4!

Mischief, mayhem and minigame madness abound in the newest Dumb Ways to Die Game.

Free to download on iOS and Android, the new Dumb Ways to Die 4 features more than 70 minigames, new locations - and even more deaths!

Think fast to save the Beans from their untimely demise, unlock new characters,, and help them rebuild Beanville!

Download the FREE game today: 
App Store: https://apps.apple.com/au/app/dumb-ways-to-die-4/id6446466397 
Play Store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=au.com.metrotrains.dwtd4&hl=en_AU&gl=US 

---
Shop Dumb Ways to Die merch: https://shop.dumbwaystodie.com/
